                                                    <h2 class="blockTitle">PRODUCTS</h2>
                                                                            <h3 class="blockSubTitle">Lower Hardware Design-In Costs</h3>
                                                                            <p class="paragraphText">Featuring RDC’s low power RISC architecture with frequency 400Mhz, the RDC R8620 processor family are building on the strength of System-on-Chip (SoC) that is x86-capable and rich peripherals including DDR3 controller, PCI-Express, SATA, USB controller, SD card, PWM, ADC, Fast Ethernet and RDC 16-bit local bus for system expansion without upgrading the whole existing hardware architecture thereby helping extend application lifetime.</p>
